(+) data sovereignty: an individual or community holding sumpreme ownership over the information they produce, 
and holding absolte authority in how the information they produce is valued, managed and monetized: 
- how it is valued, 
- who benefits from its value 
- who has access to it
→ Learn to ask, "What data/knowledge do I have that others don't?"
